		How to write a programme or a code:
		<ol>
			<li>Write an algorithm before writing of any code
				<ol>
					<li>an algorithm is a step by step process of describing any process</li>
				</ol>
			</li>
			<li>After writing an algorithm make a flowchart
				<ol>
					<li>A flow chart is a describing of procedure using tabular flow or graphical respresentation</li>
				</ol>
			</li>
			<li>After making of a flowchart, using both algorithm and flow chart try to make a simple code and take the help of the programming language syntax</li>
		</ol>
